&lt;div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 100%;&quot; src=&quot;https://info.rfsmart.com/hubfs/EVP/EVP%20statement.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Agile Delivery Specialist ( Scrum Master)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;US East Office (Jacksonville, FL)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(186, 55, 42);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;We exist to transform our customers and change lives.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335557856&amp;quot;:16777215,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We&#39;re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;RF-SMART is seeking a Agile Delivery Specialist (Scrum Master)&amp;nbsp;to join our Products group in our US East Office located in Jacksonville, FL, as we continue to grow. This role is responsible for guiding, motivating, and leading a software development team. Technical expertise, strategic experience, and strong leadership skills are all expected from this important role. The Agile Delivery Specialist&amp;nbsp;will help our Products Team accomplish its goals and directly impact our ability to accomplish our mission by helping to deliver our software products to the marketplace.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comprehensive understanding of agile methodologies&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support 2-4 Agile Development teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee process and coach the team; ensure the process is followed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Document and communicate expectations, investigate problems, and drive team to resolutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Guide and share team-oriented behaviors and interactions&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Facilitate Scrum meetings to ensure full team engagement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Remove impediments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Report on team KPIs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop detailed work plans, schedules, project estimates, resource plans, and status reports&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interfaces with product leadership regarding status of deadlines, throughput metrics, and roadmap progress&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Recommend&amp;nbsp;and oversee process improvements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Has considerable business impact through in-depth evaluation of complex business processes, system processes, and industry standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide expertise in Agile and understands the principles of Product leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Possess a comprehensive understanding of how Sales, Services, Support, and Products work together to contribute toward achieving business objectives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Directly impact the business by influencing strategic process decisions through advice, counsel, or provided services&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as an advisor or coach to newer members of the team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide in-depth and sophisticated analysis with interpretive thinking to define problems and develop innovative solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Persuade and influence others through comprehensive communication and diplomacy skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h2 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;max-width: 100%;&quot; src=&quot;https://info.rfsmart.com/hubfs/EVP/EVP%20statement.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;Associate &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18pt;&quot;&gt;Solutions Consultant&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h4 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;US East (Jacksonville, FL preferred) or US West (Highlands Ranch, CO preferred)&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Remote&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335557856&amp;quot;:16777215,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt; will be considered with prior remote experience&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;h3 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(186, 55, 42);&quot; data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;We exist to transform our customers and change lives.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335557856&amp;quot;:16777215,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more than 40 years, RF-SMART, a United States headquartered company, has delivered advanced software solutions for distributors, manufacturers, and retailers worldwide. We are growing our team and creating two early-career opportunities for individuals who are curious, eager to learn, and excited about solving real-world operational challenges for customers. If you are looking to break into the supply chain software industry and build a career at the intersection of supply chain technology and customer success — this could be the role for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Who We&#39;re Looking For:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an Associate Solutions Consultant, you will be at the heart of how RF-SMART delivers value — learning the product, serving customers, and building the foundation for a long-term career at the intersection of supply chain technology and customer success. This is not a passive, watch-from-the-sidelines role. From day one, you will learn by doing alongside experienced consultants and salespeople who are invested in your growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are hiring two associates to develop into well-rounded professionals who deeply understand our software, our customers, and the operational challenges we help solve. No prior ERP or warehouse management experience is required — we will teach you everything you need to know.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Both associates will start with Consulting Services, building product expertise and implementation experience side by side. Over time, career paths will evolve — potentially with one or both associates moving into a Customer Education focus on our Solutions Consulting team or continuing to advance within Consulting Services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are looking for a role that will accelerate your growth, challenge you daily, and put you in front of real customers solving real problems — this is it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;What You&#39;ll Do:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Consulting Services&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Shadow and support experienced consultants during live implementations, building the product fluency that underpins everything else you will do here&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop hands-on knowledge of RF-SMART&#39;s integration with ERP systems like Oracle NetSuite, learning how software maps to real warehouse and manufacturing operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in discovery calls that uncover customer challenges and

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;max-width: 100%;&quot; src=&quot;https://info.rfsmart.com/hubfs/EVP/EVP%20statement.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business Development Internship - Fall 2026&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h4 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;US East Office (Jacksonville, FL)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(186, 55, 42);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We exist to transform our customers and change lives&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We&#39;re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Business Development Intern is responsible for supporting the Marketing team in generating new business opportunities by contacting and developing relationships with potential customers. Your primary function is to nurture marketing leads through email and other channels, as well as to maintain all data accurately in CRM (NetSuite). You will join a team of marketing professionals focused on transforming more Customers and changing more lives. The intern will be reporting to the Jacksonville, FL office.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Details of the Internship:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Duration:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;8/17/2026 - 12/11/2026&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hours: &lt;/strong&gt;20-25&amp;nbsp;hours/week&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pay:&lt;/strong&gt; $20 per hour&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;x_elementToProof&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-olk-copy-source=&quot;MessageBody&quot;&gt;Demand Generation &amp;amp; Prospecting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul data-editing-info=&quot;{&amp;quot;applyListStyleFromLevel&amp;quot;:true}&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Support sales revenue goals by executing demand generation campaigns across multiple outreach channels&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Research and identify potential customers by analyzing target industries, company profiles, and key decision-makers to build qualified prospect lists&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Initiate outreach to prospective customers through email, phone, and LinkedIn, crafting personalized messaging that speaks to their specific business challenges&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;x_elementToProof&quot;&gt;Support inbound and outbound lead generation efforts to determine fit against RF-SMART&#39;s ideal customer profile (ICP)&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Assist in developing outreach sequences and cadences that improve response rates and move prospects through the funnel&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;x_elementToProof&quot;&gt;Lead Nurturing &amp;amp; Relationship Building&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul data-editing-info=&quot;{&amp;quot;applyListStyleFromLevel&amp;quot;:true}&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Build trusted relationships with prospective customers through consistent, thoughtful communication across the full nurture cycle&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Monitor prospect engagement signals — email opens, content downloads, website activity — and use those insights to time and tailor follow-up outreach&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Support the team in moving marketing-qualified leads (MQLs) toward sales-qualified leads (SQLs) through strategic touchpoints&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;x_elementToProof&quot;&gt;Learn and apply sales strategies and techniques to better understand prospect pain points and position RF-SMART&#39;s value effectively&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;x_elementToProof&quot;&gt;CRM &a

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;max-width: 100%;&quot; src=&quot;https://info.rfsmart.com/hubfs/EVP/EVP%20statement.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Business Development Manager&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h4 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Department:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt; Marketing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;h4 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Location:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt; USE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt; (Jacksonville, FL)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;h4 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Reports To:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt; Global Director of Business Development&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(186, 55, 42);&quot;&gt;We exist to transform our customers and change lives&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We&#39;re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;RF-SMART is hiring a Business Development Manager who will lead and develop a high-performing BDR team while driving strategic pipeline growth for our SaaS business lines. This is a leadership role for someone who combines modern sales methodology, data-driven decision-making, and a genuine investment in people development. The ideal candidate brings B2B SaaS sales leadership experience, a consultative approach to outbound strategy, and the ability to build a BDR function that is targeted and impactful - all in service of RF-SMART&#39;s mission to transform our Customers and change lives.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;heading 3&quot;&gt;What &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;heading 3&quot;&gt;You’ll&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;heading 3&quot;&gt; Be Doing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134245418&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134245529&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:281,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:281}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Team Leadership &amp;amp; Coaching&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct structured weekly 1:1s, coaching sessions, call-shadowing sessions, and objection-handling workshops to accelerate individual skill development&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage sales enablement platforms

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;max-width: 100%;&quot; src=&quot;https://info.rfsmart.com/hubfs/EVP/EVP%20statement.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business Development Representative&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;US East Office (Jacksonville, FL)&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(186, 55, 42);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We Exist to Transform our Customers and Change Lives&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We&#39;re Looking For&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;The Sales &amp;amp; Marketing Business Development Representative is responsible for generating new business opportunities by contacting and developing relationships with potential customers. Your primary function is to qualify marketing leads as sales opportunities through calls and emails, as well as to maintain all data accurately in CRM (NetSuite). You will join a team of marketing leaders focused on transforming more customers and changing more lives.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support sales revenue goals by executing demand generation campaigns, including inbound lead qualification, prospecting and nurturing:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Outbound Lead Qualification: Engage with sales inquiry or online chat to qualify them as sales ready, update CRM and route to sales as appropriate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Email Prospecting: Contact potential customers through calls and emails&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead Nurturing: Build trusting relationship with prospective customers through regular email touchpoints, routing them to sales once ready to engage in sales cycle&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct initial qualification, identifying client needs and position appropriate products/services&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set up meetings or calls between prospective customers and sales team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage and maintain quality of NetSuite database&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare and analyze a variety of lead reports in both CRM and Excel&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Bring:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s Degree or equivalent marketing and sales experience preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong written communication skills&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent interpersonal, presentation, email, and phone skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficient in and a minimum of four (4) years of experience using Microsoft Office applications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must work well independently, be able to prioritize and meet deadlines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent organizational and time management skills with the ability to multi-task&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be creative, energetic, extremely organized and detail-oriented&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with NetSuite CRM is preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h5&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Employer does not sponsor applicants for employment visa status (e.g. H-1B visa status).&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;h5&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;General Information:&amp;nbsp; The above noted job description is not intended to be an exhaustive list of all duties and responsibilities that may be assigned, but rather t

&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;max-width: 100%;&quot; src=&quot;https://info.rfsmart.com/hubfs/EVP/EVP%20statement.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Customer Success Consultant (ERP)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;US East, US West, or US distributed from other geographies in the US will be considered&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(186, 55, 42);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We exist to transform our customers and change lives&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We’re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Are you ready to take on a dynamic role where you can make a real impact? As a Customer Success Consultant, you’ll be at the forefront of delivering cutting-edge warehouse management solutions using our innovative data collection software for NetSuite ERP. If you thrive in a fast-paced environment and love the challenge of optimizing operations, this role is for you!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:279}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;What You’ll Do:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:279}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Design &amp;amp; Deliver: Create tailored warehouse data collection solutions using RF-SMART for the NetSuite ERP application, focusing on areas like receiving, inventory control, picking, and light production.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:279}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Consult &amp;amp; Advise: Be the go-to expert for customers, guiding them on best practices in warehouse setup, receiving, and shipping.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:279}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Train &amp;amp; Support: Lead training sessions and provide ongoing support, ensuring customers are confident and successful post-Go Live.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:279}&quot;&gt; Travel averages at 30%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Hit Billable Targets: Manage your time effectively to meet billable targets, contributing to the success and profitability of the business.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:279}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
