&lt;li&gt;Basic familiarity with tools and frameworks common in front-end application development such as JavaScript, HTML, CSS, React, etc. preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Basic familiarity with databases and ability to write and understand simple SQL preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Possess an innate ability to “think outside the box” and be creative to accomplish tasks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent written and verbal communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
