&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&amp;nbsp; Jacksonville, FL, Highlands Ranch, CO or Remote&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(186, 55, 42);&quot;&gt;We exist to transform our customers and change lives&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Headquartered in Jacksonville, FL, RF-SMART® is a global software company focused on delivering world-class mobile supply chain management (SCM) applications for inventory management, manufacturing, shipping, and related supply chain arenas across industries.  If you are energized by transforming customers and changing lives by bringing software features to market that solve business problems, then RF-SMART may be right for you. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join RF-SMART as we scale our NetSuite WMS platform serving customers worldwide. As Senior Product Director, you&#39;ll lead a team of 10 + product leaders focused on product vision and strategy that powers critical warehouse and manufacturing operations, helping businesses move, track, and fulfill millions of items daily with speed and accuracy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this senior leadership role, you&#39;ll own product strategy for B2B SaaS platforms focused on warehouse management, manufacturing execution, and mobile operational workflows. You&#39;ll build and mentor a high-performing product team while partnering closely with Engineering, Sales, Services, and Executive Leadership to drive growth and customer value.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for a product leader who excels at&amp;nbsp;translating market insights into compelling product strategy, developing high-performing teams, and driving alignment across diverse stakeholders—all while maintaining focus on customer value and business outcomes.&lt;/p&gt;
