&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own product vision, strategy, and roadmap for WMS, Manufacturing, and Mobile solutions, aligned to company growth objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understand market trends and competitive landscape to identify unique value propositions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop product packaging and licensing to maximize customer value and revenue.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee the development of compelling product narratives that clearly communicate customer value and competitive advantage.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure strong integration and alignment with ERP systems as systems of record.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Leadership &amp;amp; Team Development&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead, mentor, and develop Product Managers and Product Owners.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish and reinforce product management best practices, including discovery, prioritization, outcome-based road mapping, and customer validation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build a high-trust, high-accountability product culture focused on customer value and business impact.&lt;/li&gt;
